Hartelijk dank.

98
00:11:57,168 --> 00:12:02,348
Wat is het? Jongen: chocolade. Chocolade.

99
00:12:02,549 --> 00:12:05,175
Jongen: Ja, chocolade, chocolade, chocolade Shri Mataji.

100
00:12:05,376 --> 00:12:09,110
Dank je. Dank je zeer.

101
00:12:14,839 --> 00:12:17,451
Dank je.

102
